
<div class="col-md-offset-2 col-md-8 col-sm-12">
  <p class="heading-content">
  Well hot diggity dog! Here is where all your saved bills will be located with the due date of each bill.  Don't
  worry, whoever created this app is smart and built it to send a nice text message reminder a day before its due!</p>

    <table class="table table-hover">
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th class="col-md-4">Name</th>
          <th class="col-md-4">Due date</th>
          <th class="col-md-4">Remind me</th>
          <th class="col-md-4">Phone number</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>

      <tbody>
        <% current_user.bills.each do |bill| %>
        <tr>
          <td><%= bill.name %></td>
          <td><%= bill.due_date.to_s(:due_time) %></td>
          <td><%= bill.reminder.to_s(:due_time) %></td>
          <td><%= bill.phone_number %></td>

          <td><%= link_to 'Show', bill %></td>
          <td><%= link_to 'Edit', edit_bill_path(bill) %></td>
          <td><%= link_to 'Destroy', bill, method: :delete, data: { confirm: 'Are you sure?' } %></td>
        </tr>
        <% end %>
      </tbody>
    </table>
<hr>
    <p class="text-center">
      <% if user_signed_in? %>
      <%= link_to "Sign Out", destroy_user_session_path, method: 'delete' %>
      <% end %>
    </p>
</div>

